About Rainbow Six Siege X:
Rainbow Six Siege X is an exciting, new approach to the first-person shooter experience that puts tactical combat and masterful destruction at the center of the action. Lead your team of unique operators through tense and thrilling combat scenarios, and achieve victory through smart preparation and strategic improvisation. Rainbow Six Siege X is available now on Xbox, PlayStation® and PC.

About Anno 117: Pax Romana:
In the latest instalment of the award-winning Anno strategy franchise, it’s your destiny to shape the Roman Empire in the year 117 AD. As governor, will you encourage economic growth or expand your rule through dominance? Lead with rebellion or unite a diverse culture? 
The cost of peace is yours to decide.

author: Ubisoft
description:
Avatar: Frontiers of Pandora - From the Ashes, coming December 19, 2025. 
Preorder today: https://ubi.li/2zc56

Avatar: Frontiers of Pandora™ – From the Ashes is an action-adventure expansion with ties to the new Avatar: Fire and Ash film.
Experience the ultimate Pandora adventure in the Western Frontier, with new third-person gameplay offering revamped combat and improved banshee mechanics. Use stealth or go guns blazing to seek vengeance and redemption against the enemies.

Pre-order now and get the Floating Mountains bonus content, including three different color patterns to customize your banshee and immerse yourself further in the Western Frontier.

Requires the base game to play.

Play as So’lek, a Na’vi warrior who has found solace with the Sarentu. Just as peace settles over the Western Frontier, a new threat rises: the RDA, now allied with the Ash clan, who are ruthless Na’vi bent on annihilation.
